WEBVTT

00:01.480 --> 00:02.916
It's time to keep up with the sun.

00:04.001 --> 00:07.481
Let's take a look at how to stay outside for longer and make the sun your friend.

00:08.965 --> 00:11.484
Wear sunglasses to protect your eyes against the sun.

00:12.550 --> 00:14.511
Bring lots of water to stay hydrated.

00:15.009 --> 00:16.451
Tell the time with a sundial.

00:17.347 --> 00:18.547
Always wear sunscreen.

00:19.366 --> 00:22.133
Flip your frisbee over, you can use it as a plate.

00:23.040 --> 00:24.580
Cool off under a waterfall.

00:25.430 --> 00:29.128
Put your feet in the water or chill out under a palm tree.

00:30.072 --> 00:32.907
Get out in the ocean and learn to surf.

00:35.302 --> 00:38.658
Invent a game like, who can throw their shoe the farthest?

00:40.239 --> 00:43.229
Ask your old best friend to take a photo with your new best friend.

00:45.671 --> 00:50.296
Now get out there and keep up with the sun with ACG.

